{"type": "article", "id": 15793, "title": "色票日历", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-09T07:35:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135559ZNBnE3KYWv2R1bLe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t对于年轻一代来说，手撕日历似乎是很遥远的事，尤其是有了手机之后，挂历都容易被忽略了。这位来自德国的设计师 Peter von Freyhold 做了一套色票日历，一周七天是七种颜色。巧妙的是，每撕下一张，露出的颜色依然与上下不同，保持了七色彩虹的样子，寓意每一天都色彩缤纷与众不同。当撕开过去看见全新的颜色时也能重新思考今天的生活，而撕下的纸片背面也可以当做便签条。售价 42.18 美元，这里是<a href=\"http://www.vonfreyhold.com/projekte/color-swatch-calendar-2016/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的网站</a>和<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Color-Swatch-Calendar-2016/dp/B00V8BC486\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143131Cj1PG84EUX5Ypmly.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143131bf0zcugaO5dEFGnM.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143131HSuWfB8ikVgeFoQT.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"711\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261431320DBC1WtyJswimLAU.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143132YDVQeG2rRAhsiq7K.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}